Verse 1: Skengdo]
Got broski 'til the end, he's got me, that's what I call brotherly love
Sweetness feeling the tugg but I act dumb when she talk 'bout love
Chat 'bout me? Swear you must be drunk, do you wanna end up like the other mug?
No, I won't jerk my plug for grub 'cause he does nice me and it helps my jugg
See the ting there, just bruk, bruk, bruk, skid in the auto, no need for clutch
YG got him, that's too much blood, won't say no names 'cause that's way too much
Certain man think that this life is fun, think again or you might get rubbed
Madness what my bro's Lyca does, he makes more than a crack shotta does
And are you gonna back your slime? Cah the toolie finna take out mans spine
Heard that you smoked me? Lies, I'm really starting to hate these guys
Better miss me with the beef online, I ain't got time, I ride not type
Like Mostack, need a girl that shines, I curve them guys 'cause it's not like mine
Silly boy thinks he's cruddy 'til it gets real, now he's crying for Mummy
Funny, 410, my cuzzy, better fall back or we make that bloody
And I didn't go colly, I hit the streets, tryna make this money
Phone ringing off, always had man jogging, cash, no ticks, can't owe me nothing

[Verse 2: AM]
Stress tryna lock these drones, next of kin just moving all jarring
I don't even care how my uncle Phil’s, true say, my cousins Will like Carlton
And I thought Skengdo's been drinking 'cause he got the Grey Goose, that's Carson
And if feds keep locking off shows, how we gonna see O2 like Carbon?
NCP for the drone, just park it, meant what I said, stop begging me pardon
If a ting did crash, better run boy, see the Hennessy box, get rassing
Tell her "I'm NBA like YoungBoy", grabbing this rocket, I'm making it Harden
Gonna write off when I back my pencil, might affi give it a sharpen
Lil' sweetheart, do you love me? 'Cause your bredrin said that I'm ugly
But I'm strong like Wray and his nephew and the 13% like bubbly
Huh, how dare you hug me? When you lied, it was oh so lovely
In the bando, oh so comfy, it went wrong when I stepped out in a long coat for the third time in like two days
It's a M charge or it's taped off with the same colours as Ukraine
Gassed up, I'm a chemical with the same number as Butane
And the one time when it don't bang, manna Batman like Bruce Wayne


[Verse 3: Skengdo]
Me, Draco in the T, which dumb guy wanna try rob me?
Please, back my shank on a instant, it's no thinking, I do this for the casheen
This young boy getting a punishment if he don't bring back the rasclart P
And this bitch wantin' some D, well, I need somewhere to put my re
Mazzaleen when I'm with my team and top floggers hold it down for me
Jeez, I need me a fat Febreeze 'cause this T-house smelling just like weed
Corn if a man straight of with his fee, neighbours are pissed, woke up, fell asleep
No, you don't bang, you wait in the T, why did you lie? You ain't onto me

[Verse 4: AM]
Du-du, du-du, baby, relax, she giving me hat
One in the head, one in the clip, she Hannibal Lecter, swallowing kids
Talk about love, don't care how you feel, I'm looking for spots, Cruella de Vil
Leave me alone, I don't wanna chill, du-du, du-du, still in the field (Bumbaclart)
See a Cargo like Shoreditch, anytime we see them in traffic
And I don't know nuttin' bout foreskin, I just pull it back and then slap it
Free Slapit, Bunny yute like a rabbit
She feeling me and I grab it
Jeet, jeet, then I vanish

[Outro]
(Brigade)
